title: Residential, Educational, Institutional, Assembly, Business, Mercantile, Industrial, Storage, information Technology, Recreational
clause_text: Residential, Educational, Institutional, Assembly, Business, Mercantile, Industrial, Storage, information Technology, Recreational. Any other land use as may be made permissible by the Government of India within SEZ. The following uses shall be permissible in this zone. Airport and allied activities and services incidental thereto.
